content: Worth re-reading Tim on NFT anonymity-Elsie purchased the «Edicurial» domain name for her art collection already in 2017-around same time as CryptoPunk launch in 2017&allowed her to b well-prepared for the explosion of creativity on blockchain last year. https://t.co/AChR69U1Wz https://t.co/ZZyLxVzcA3 https://t.co/nQMs9icN3t
